|align=center|''khenen'' ||align=center|<hiero>D33:N35-N35:E21-A24  </hiero>||align=center | pertuber,<br /> tumulte
|-
|align=center| ''qeri'' ||align=center|<hiero>N29:D21-M17-E21  </hiero>||align=center | orage,<br /> nuage
